FEATURES
* Configurable path for downloaded torrents
* Change iconset
* Allow to mark an episode as new again (as opposed to mark it as downloaded)
* Make torrent page into a javascript overlay window - no need to load a different page just for this
* General error handling (display errors and messages on page, field validation, etc)

CODE
* Introduce spring-data
* Use java-based configuration instead of XML based
* separation of concerns - logic is spread between controller, service and model. everything should be unified in services
* Unit testing